org.daisy.common.xproc.calabash.impl

Class DynamicXProcConfigurationFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.daisy.common.xproc.calabash.impl.DynamicXProcConfigurationFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    XProcConfigurationFactory, XProcStepRegistry
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DynamicXProcConfigurationFactory_SPI

    public class DynamicXProcConfigurationFactory
extends Object
implements XProcConfigurationFactory, XProcStepRegistry
    Mainly thought to be used throught OSGI this class creates configuration objects used with the calabash engine wrapper.
